# NEMETIC STRING
# Human_Enhancement_Ethics (C142)

Φ(Human_Enhancement_Ethics) = σ(access|exclusion) ∘ ρ(elevation|inequality) ∘ λ(transcendence|hubris) ∘ β(evolution|fragmentation) ∘ δγ(grounding|unmooring) ∘ μ(augmentation|erosion) + ε | :dialectical_tension

# OPERATOR BREAKDOWN
# σ(access|exclusion)          :: Air  :: Who controls access determines liberation vs entrenchment
# ρ(elevation|inequality)      :: Water :: Enhancement risks creating biological castes
# λ(transcendence|hubris)      :: Fire  :: Promethean flame of self-improvement burns with creative destruction
# β(evolution|fragmentation)   :: Wood  :: Unchecked growth fragments the forest of shared humanity
# δγ(grounding|unmooring)      :: Earth :: Enhancement threatens to unmoor identity from biological continuity
# μ(augmentation|erosion)      :: Metal :: Enhancement augments capabilities but may erode character-shaping struggle
